Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.71,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}優しさなんていらない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:03.42,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}冷たい風に胸が凍えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:07.80,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}熱い誓いを見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:16.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}いまはただ走るだけと頷いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:21.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}すべて許しあえる日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:26.82,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}来るのなら　信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.11,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fs48}（来るときを）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.33,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}哀しみが時代を駆ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.37,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}思い出を抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:41.25,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}魂に触れたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:45.59,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}すれ違うならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.09,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}同じ願いを追いかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:58.44,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}流星になって燃えようか
Comment: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:54.54,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}不要用语言让我生出幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:58.71,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}我无须你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:03.42,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}凛冽的寒风把我的心冻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:07.80,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}眼里燃烧着誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:16.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}现在你我心照不宣  只需奋力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:21.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}接受彼此一切的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:26.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}若是会到来  我坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.11,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\fs57}（一定会到来）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}悲伤穿梭于整个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.37,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}让我们牢记这段记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:41.25,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}想要触摸彼此心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.38,0:22:45.59,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}即使擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:50.09,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}也要追逐同一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:58.44,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}化作流星  点亮光明
